# Local runtime data — never publish. Real data lives in ~/.drishti & ~/.claude
# (outside this repo); these patterns are defense-in-depth in case the data dir
# is ever pointed at the repo (e.g. DRISHTI_DATA_DIR=.) during development.
*.db
*.db-wal
*.db-shm
*.sqlite
*.sqlite3
*.env
.env
/security-rules.toml

# AI / workflow artifacts — kept local, never published
.claude/
.superpowers/
CLAUDE.md
docs/superpowers/
Drishti-TECH-SPEC.md
docs/*.dc.html
